snippet.title: Song of Iron - Xbox Summer Showcase 2020 - Extended Trailer 4k/60fps
snippet.description:
Consider Subscribing! - https://tinyurl.com/Sub-to-Song-of-Iron
Find more at - https://www.songofiron.com/

My name is Joe and I am so excited to finally announce Song of Iron is coming to XBOX Series X and XBOX ONE!!! 

"Song of Iron is a moody and provoking action adventure. A dive into a dark Nordic world full of mystery and danger. Your journey will take you far across the land of myths toward the home of the gods. Fight your way through man, monster and nature itself to reach the end."



---Join the Song of Iron party!---
Twitter - https://twitter.com/SongofIron
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/song_of_iron/
Discord - https://www.discord.gg/GqtgsmC

Wish-list Song of Iron on steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1258220/Song_of_Iron/?beta=0


music by www.willgoss.com
sound design http://strikecastaudio.com/
